p: Taking into account the chemical content range, a correlation network based on components from EO of this species is shown in Figure 5b. There were strong negative correlations between terpinen-4-ol and β-pinene as well as β-pinene and borneol. Positive correlations are noted between terpinen-4-ol and borneol, as well as multiple correlation between allo-aromadendrene, epi- α-cadinol and α-cadinol.
